mediaDetails.ext_alt_text: Top: Redraw your old art! @KianaMosser Left: 2004 illustration of Pichu on a card made of regular paper. Pichu is standing in a sunny field with its mouth open. The lines and colors appear to have been drawn with a shaky hand. Right: 2024 redraw of the Pichu card, digital, using a template resembling the official cards. Pichu is looking up in the sky at a rainbow, surrounded by flowers. Two Cutiefly are also looking up. The wind is blowing, causing flower petals and dandelion seeds to float. Skiploom and Hoppip are flying through the air. Card text: Kiana's Pichu, 40 HP. Baby Pokemon. Pikabolt, 10. Pichu does 10 damage to itself. This is a fanmade card. Not legal for use in official play.
